method.description:
Informs whether the component was selected by the dependency substitution rule.
Users can configure dependency substitution rules via <a href='type://org.gradle.api.artifacts.ResolutionStrategy#getDependencySubstitution()'>org.gradle.api.artifacts.ResolutionStrategy#getDependencySubstitution()</a>

@since 1.4

